videos.description: Glenn Smith returns the opening kickoff 93 yards for the Georgia State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_GSU (Smith gets Georgia State off and running with a TD)

videos.headline: Smith gets Georgia State off and running with a TD

videos.description: Penny Hart scores on a 7-yard touchdown pass play to push Georgia State's lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Hart's TD catch extends lead for Georgia State

videos.description: Tyler Keane and Omar Black connect from 33 yards out for a touchdown to put Coastal Carolina on the board.
videos.headline: Keane to Black puts Coastal Carolina on the board

videos.description: Kyler Neal scores on a 3-yard run to push the lead to 14 in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Neal bulldozes into the endzone for another Georgia State TD

videos.description: Tyler Keane connects with Chris Jones for a 22 yard pass play for a Coastal Carolina first down in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Keane and Jones connect for big gain

videos.description: Tyler Keane hits Ky'Jon Tyler for a 5 yard touchdown to close the deficit for Coastal Carolina.
videos.headline: Keane TD pass narrows deficit for Coastal Carolina

videos.description: Conner Manning hits Ari Werts for a 52 yard pass play that puts Georgia State in Coastal Carolina territory.
videos.headline: Manning finds Werts for a huge gain

videos.description: DeMarcus Kirk's 4 yard touchdown run extends the lead for Georgia State in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Georgia State answers Coastal Carolina with a TD

videos.description: Tyler Keane hits Larry Collins Jr. for a 5 yard touchdown to close the gap for Coastal Carolina.
videos.headline: Keane TD pass cuts into the Georgia State lead
